                        <div class="sched_1_left py-5 px-4 bg_light text-center">
                            <hr class="line mx-auto mt-0">
                            <b class="d-block fs-2 mt-3 mb-3">Chef James Thew</b>
                            <p>James Thew is a renowned chef at a five-star hotel, known for his signature recipes and TV appearances. Passionate about cooking, he also runs weekend cookery classes to share his culinary skills and connect with food lovers.</p>
                            <ul class="mb-0 bg-white w-75 mx-auto">
                                <li class="d-flex">
                                    <span class="bg_red text-white fs-1 d-inline-block span_1"><i class="bi-telephone"></i></span>
                                    <span class="text-start p-3">
                                        <b class="d-block text-muted font_14 mt-1">For Contact 24/7</b>
                                        <b class="d-block mt-1 fs-4">+214312890</b>
                                    </span>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col p-0">
                        <div class="sched_1_mid">
                            <img src="~/ClientCss/images/icons-svg/james.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt="abc">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col p-0">
                        <div class="sched_1_right py-5 px-5 bg_red">
                            <p id="txt">Beyond the kitchen, James Thew inspires food enthusiasts through his bestselling recipe books, TV shows, and interactive sessions. His creative flair and love for experimenting with flavors make him a favorite among aspiring chefs and home cooks alike.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>

